02:38.948 --> 02:42.001
I'm working on the new me.

02:42.081 --> 02:44.082
I was on my way home.

02:44.083 --> 02:46.818
Thought I'd stop by your place,
see how you're doing.

02:48.587 --> 02:50.455
So... how you doing?

02:50.456 --> 02:52.023
I hate jogging.

02:52.024 --> 02:53.858
Your dog wouldn't let me
cross the bridge.

02:54.111 --> 02:55.773
Apparently, he's not a jogger.

02:56.634 --> 02:58.201
And you are?

02:59.036 --> 03:01.605
I was, for a while.

03:01.606 --> 03:03.640
Can you come into Boston
tomorrow?

03:03.641 --> 03:05.175
I'm pretty busy.

03:05.176 --> 03:07.277
I'll check my schedule.

03:07.278 --> 03:09.446
See if you can squeeze it in.

03:09.447 --> 03:10.981
How about a ride?

03:10.982 --> 03:12.582
It's unlocked.

03:28.065 --> 03:30.267
(thunder rumbling)

03:37.141 --> 03:39.743
(sighs)

04:02.967 --> 04:05.035
(explosions booming on TV)

04:05.036 --> 04:07.370
(train chugging)

04:07.371 --> 04:10.173
(gunfire, man grunting on TV)

04:13.811 --> 04:15.612
You.

04:16.447 --> 04:19.349
You.

04:19.350 --> 04:22.285
(train whistle blowing on TV)

04:22.286 --> 04:24.488
(explosion booming)

04:28.392 --> 04:29.826
What have I done?

04:29.827 --> 04:32.028
(train chugging,
whistle blowing)

04:33.531 --> 04:37.200
(booming)

04:39.170 --> 04:41.337
(train chugging)

04:45.710 --> 04:47.844
(train whistle blowing)

04:51.015 --> 04:53.650
(whistle blowing repeatedly)

04:57.822 --> 05:00.023
